  "title": "Management Executive 4/5/8 Off Days per month",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<p>· To undergo management Training for Front of House (Floor) and Back of House (Kitchen)</p>\n<p>·Lead and manage a high performance team and develop talents</p>\n<p>·Attend customer's needs and queries</p>\n<p>·Handle and resolve customer complaints</p>\n<p>·Provide management and administrative support</p>\n<p>·Assist Managers complete daily tasks and overseas an efficient and effective day to day operation of branch or outlet</p>\n<p>·Monitors in ensuring a clean and safe working environment</p>\n<p>·Assist manager in recruitment, training and marketing campaign</p>\n<p>·Coach and develop colleagues to ensure meet standard of operation</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<p>· Diploma in Management, Business, Hospitality and relevant fields</p>\n<p>· Strong management skills with ability to lead and manage a team</p>\n<p>· High energy and strong interpersonal skills</p>\n<p>· Well-groomed and professional appearance</p>\n<p>· Strong verbal and written communication skills</p>\n<p>· Able to work shift, weekends and public holiday</p>",
